        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 5. Male and female genital anatomy of Songthela yuping sp. nov. A, D palp prolateral view B, E palp ventral view C, F palp retrolateral view G palp distal view H-K vulva dorsal view L-O vulva ventral view A-G XUX- 2018 - 380 A (holotype) H, L XUX- 2018 - 380 I, M XUX- 2018 - 374 J, N XUX- 2018 - 377 K, O XUX- 2018 - 382 P, T XUX- 2018 - 382 A Q, U XUX- 2018 - 375 R, V XUX- 2018 - 379 S, W XUX- 2018 - 373. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." , "Figure 4. Male and female genital anatomy of Songthela tianzhu sp. nov. A, D palp prolateral view B, E palp ventral view C, F palp retrolateral view G palp distal view H-K vulva dorsal view L-O vulva ventral view A-G XUX- 2018 - 340 A (holotype) H, L XUX- 2018 - 339 I, M XUX- 2018 - 338 J, N XUX- 2018 - 340 K, O XUX- 2018 - 341. Scale bars: 0.3 mm." , "Figure 3. Male and female genital anatomy of Songthela liui sp. nov. A, D palp prolateral view B, E palp ventral view C, G palp retrolateral view H palp distal view I-L vulva dorsal view M-P vulva ventral view A-H XUX- 2018 - 375 A (holotype) I, M XUX- 2018 - 381 J, N XUX- 2018 - 383 A K, O XUX- 2018 - 387 D L, P XUX- 2018 - 387. Scale bars: 0.3 mm (A-E, G-P); 0.1 mm (F)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/542519" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/542518" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/542517" .

